BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:leadflow-annual-strategy-2027@leadflow-pro.local
DTSTART:20270120T100000Z
DTEND:20270120T140000Z
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY;BYMONTH=1;BYDAY=3TU
SUMMARY:LeadFlowPro: Annual Dependency Strategy Review
DESCRIPTION:ANNUAL REVIEW - Set aside 4 hours\n\nTier 1 Major Version Discussion:\n- React 19→20 upgrade path?\n- Express 4→5 decision\n- Prisma 7→8 timeline\n- Node.js LTS upgrade strategy\n\nDeliverables:\n- Update 12-month upgrade roadmap\n- Document migration paths\n- Update DEPENDENCY_STRATEGY.md with new targets\n\nNOTE: Occurs on 3rd Tuesday of January
LOCATION:LeadFlowPro Project
PRIORITY:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CATEGORIES:Development,DevOps,Strategy
END:VEVENT

